      "content": "hey, im a fitness coach and im workin on some new programming for a diverse group of clients. i want to be as precise as possible with how i tailor training. from a sports science perspective, are there any actual biological differences in stuff like muscle fiber composition or athletic potential that vary between different racial groups? just trying to make sure my programming is optimized for everyone.",
